title: Vinnie Vincent Invasion
description:
Here is the awesome Vinnie Vincent uploaded by me to make up for those dorks who uploaded before but never finished seeding.  If you love metal and good guitar riffs, then you&#039;ll love these guys.  This is good fun hair band metal from the 80&#039;s.

Like other stuff in my collection, I bought these first on vinyl, then on cassette, and now on CD.  Gotta love those fucking music companies complaining about filesharing while they expect you to pay three times for the same product.

Anyway, if you&#039;re new to Vinnie and crew and you like the test drive, please buy the albums to support the band.  And don&#039;t forget to help seed after you download.

This contains 2 albums: "Invasion" and "All Systems Go", both remastered versions.
